longBusinessSummary: Foresight Financial Group, Inc., together with its subsidiaries, provides various banking services to individuals and businesses in the United States. Its deposit products include demand deposits and certificates of deposit; and loan portfolio comprises agricultural, agribusiness, commercial, real estate, and installment loans. Foresight Financial Group, Inc. was founded in 1986 and is based in Winnebago, Illinois.
